com.hamweather.aeris.tiles

Enum AerisPointData

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AerisPointData>
      • com.hamweather.aeris.tiles.AerisPointData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AerisPointData>

    public enum AerisPointData
extends java.lang.Enum<AerisPointData>
    Aeris point enum that helps setup each loading with the proper aeris query, proper handler and proper legend. Legends can be overriden by using their own drawable in the same name.
    Author:
    bcollins
